Livestock Population and Production Online 	Software(LPPOS) enables the RARDA animal production unit to have the number of animals they manage by race, in each district, province and whole country.
LPPOS populate Livestock in two categories; Live and Dead animals since both statistics has an important implication to Rwanda Animal Resources Development Authority.
LPPOS enables to know Livestock Production from different Animals (Milk,meat,eggs,honey,skins,hides ). The quantity of this production is always measured in tons.
Livestock production counts both the quantity consummed and this on market.This process ignores household consumption. Milk are collected through milk collection centers, meats collected through slaug

